init_text: You're Barack Obama. 4 years into your retirement, you awake to find a letter with no return address on your bedside table. It reads "I hope you've had a chance to relax Barack...but pack your bags and call the number below. It's time to start the real job." Signed simply, "JFK."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I called it from a burner phone and a man answered.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He didn't say who he was but asked if I had the letter that was left on my bedside table.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Once I arrived, the coordinates pointed me to an abandoned warehouse.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It was an older man with a ring on his finger.

actions.name: text-delete
actions.text: was an older man with a ring on his finger.
